  concatMap(([project, sites]) =&gt; {
    const siteId = /* whatever here */;
    return GetPersons(siteId);
  }),
).subscribe(...);

```
It also depends on whether you want to receive in the observer all responses or just the last one. If you want all responses then you&#39;ll need to chain `GetPersons` with `map` and append the first two responses:

```
GetPersons(siteId).pipe(
